Ahkiyyini in borrowed flesh~
A nude, unwashed woman with loose and saggy skin stands before you with outstretched arms and empty eye sockets. 
~
   Everything about this woman is wrong.  Her hair is a silvery white that
appears healthy and lush in contrast to all other aspects of this womans
appearance.  Smooth, fleshy eye sockets are surrounded by caked grime-covered
saggy skin.  Mossy-green rotten teeth are set in her saggy jowls that tremble
as she moves.  The rest of her body is as caked with dirt and sweat as her
face, and her breasts are deflated and empty.  She looks like she is wearing
the borrowed skin of someone who was much larger.  The nails on her hands and
feet are overgrown and dirty, but sharp enough to be weapons.  Her ragged
breath exudes a cloud of revolting air.  She sniffs the air around her.  
~
