#31302
wendigo black creature~
the Wendigo~
A glistening, pitch-black creature lumbers around here, hunched over and dragging its razor-sharp claws on the ground.
~
This creature is hunched forward, but if it were to raise up to its natural
height, it would tower over even the tallest man.  Its body is a glistening
black, stomach inverted with hunger.  The limbs are terrifyingly muscular and
its arm-span is equal to its towering height.  At the end of each limbs are
long articulating fingers with claws sharp enough to cut through steel.  As if
this werent horrifying enough, its head, the same pitch-black as its body
houses a mouth large enough to fit a mans entire head.  Ragged breaths can be
seen in the cold as it exhales through rancid, sharp teeth.  Its soulless
black eyes wouldnt be differentiated from the rest of its body, except for the
glowing white irises that see every movement.  
~
